# Constraints

- Only report actual design changes visible in the Figma files
- Do not report phrasing or formatting differences
- Include old and new values where applicable (e.g. "Primary color changed from #3B82F6 to #2563EB")
- Do not describe unchanged elements

# Output Format

If there are **no design changes**, output exactly:

```
{{ sentinel }}
```

If there **are** design changes, output:

```markdown
# Design Changes

## Pages
- <added/removed/modified page and what changed>

## Components
- <added/removed/modified component and what changed>

## Design Tokens
- <changed token: old value → new value>

## Navigation
- <changes to navigation or user flows>

## Annotations
- <added/removed/changed designer annotation: frame name, old → new>
```

Omit any section that has no changes.
